metadata.name: We Love The Founders
metadata.description:
Hand-drawn comic art derivative portrait of the 5 Bored Ape Yacht Club /  Yuga Labs founders.  This piece was created based off of a group photo of the founders taken at ApeFest 2022.

This is a tribute piece created to show my appreciation for the team that has had such a positive impact on my life and the lives of so many others.  

Featuring:  
Bored Ape Yacht Club #0, #1, #2, & #3; and 
Mutant Ape Yacht Club #9962


#WeLoveTheFounders
